cting seasons or special events.\\nAccess to N Seoul Tower is part of the experience—visitors can hike, take a cable car, or ride a bus up Namsan Mountain, adding a touch of nature and leisure tourism to the visit. From a tourism management perspective, the attraction demonstrates strong destination branding, accessibility, and visitor experience design, though it can become crowded during peak hours.", "languageCode": "en"}, "rating": 5, "publishTime": "2025-12-30T15:17:44.149149533Z", "originalText": {"text": "N Seoul Tower, also known as Namsan Tower, is one of Seoul’s most iconic landmarks and a symbol of the city’s blend of nature, romance, and urban life. Located atop Namsan Mountain, the tower offers spectacular panoramic views of Seoul, making it especially popular during sunset and nighttime when the city lights come alive.\\nOne of its most famous features is the Love Locks area, where couples attach padlocks as a symbol of lasting love, creating a romantic and memorable atmosphere. The observation deck provides clear views in all directions, while restaurants and cafés inside the tower allow visitors to enjoy dining with a skyline backdrop. The tower’s LED lighting changes colors at night, often reflecting seasons or special events.\\nAccess to N Seoul Tower is part of the experience—visitors can hike, take a cable car, or ride a bus up Namsan Mountain, adding a touch of nature and leisure tourism to the visit. From a tourism management perspective, the attraction demonstrates strong destination branding, accessibility, and visitor experience design, though it can become crowded during peak hours.", "languageCode": "en"}, "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kdmRWRlpPRkEyYUVGRlozVlFaRWMzVmtnd09HYxAB!2m1!1s0x357ca257a88e6aa9:0x5cf8577c2e7982a5", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kdmRWRlpPRkEyYUVGRlozVlFaRWMzVmtnd09HYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "authorAttribution": {"uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113975822305913974789/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgoe-39g0Tqr1Cjy6Fip-e1Y6oHdRVhyAy4hRFK0WVpiNpucQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5", "displayName": "ARMANDO HISUAN"}, "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a week ago"}, {"name": "places/ChIJqWqOqFeifDURpYJ5LnxX-Fw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25VemVVOVdhRVF4V1UxV1Z6aDVTRWxRVlUxTlNVRRAB", "text": {"text": "~throw back to 7th November 2025~\\n\\nThis place is huge and absolutely beautiful!\\nN Seoul Tower is located on top of a mountain, and you can either hike up or take the cable car.\\nPersonally, the cable car experience wasn’t that great. there wasn’t much scenery to enjoy, and it was quite crowded, so it didn’t really feel worth it.\\n\\nHowever, the area around the tower is really nice, with plenty of things to see and many great photo spots.\\nEverything is worth exploring.\\n\\nWe were also lucky enough to catch a traditional performance during our visit.\\n\\nOverall, it’s definitely worth going to see!", "languageCode": "en"}, "rating": 5, "publishTime": "2025-12-24T06:47:49.995736713Z", "originalText": {"text": "~throw back to 7th November 2025~\\n\\nThis place is huge and absolutely beautiful!\\nN Seoul Tower is located on top of a mountain, and you can either hike up or take the cable car.\\nPersonally, the cable car experience wasn’t that great. there wasn’t much scenery to enjoy, and it was quite crowded, so it didn’t really feel worth it.\\n\\nHowever, the area around the tower is really nice, with plenty of things to see and many great photo spots.\\nEverything is worth exploring.\\n\\nWe were also lucky enough to catch a traditional performance during our visit.\\n\\nOverall, it’s definitely worth going to see!", "languageCode": "en"}, "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25VemVVOVdhRVF4V1UxV1Z6aDVTRWxRVlUxTlNVRRAB!2m1!1s0x357ca257a88e6aa9:0x5cf8577c2e7982a5", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25VemVVOVdhRVF4V1UxV1Z6aDVTRWxRVlUxTlNVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "authorAttribution": {"uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112691711565360237621/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmDR1XmjGgSXSoOrdh5IHyqJUh09XSWWWsrKisS3xA9YLrbQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6", "displayName": "Sshhtt 1015"}, "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 weeks ago"}, {"name": "places/ChIJqWqOqFeifDURpYJ5LnxX-Fw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GZlpuVmZlR3M0YTBWV2FEWnBlVGxQUm5CZlRrRRAB", "text": {"text": "I hiked up to Seoul North Tower and walked all 1,000 stairs to the top. The trail is beautiful with all the fall colors and the air feels so fresh. Someone even marked the stair count along the way, which kept me going. I went up for the 5:15 sunset and I was definitely ambitious because I barely made it on time. The view over Seoul is absolutely breathtaking.\\n\\nThe stairs are very well maintained and there are little resting spots every few minutes. At the top there is a plaza, a 7-Eleven, and a restaurant. After watching the sunset it got dark really fast, and that’s when I realized I couldn’t get an Uber to come up. I panicked a bit because the only way down was by bus and I had no money on my T-money card. I managed to reload it at the 7-Eleven and just hopped on the first bus going down the mountain. When it gets dark there, it is really dark.\\n\\nWhat an adventure. It was an amazing hike and I highly recommend it. Just make sure your T-money card has enough balance if you stay late! 😅", "languageCode": "en"}, "rating": 5, "publishTime": "2025-11-24T06:10:55.621768017Z", "originalText": {"text": "I hiked up to Seoul North Tower and walked all 1,000 stairs to the top. The trail is beautiful with all the fall colors and the air feels so fresh. Someone even marked the stair count along the way, which kept me goi