itors through about 1,400 years of Islamic culture, think calligraphy, geometric designs, ceramics, textiles, and architectural details. Honestly, it feels pretty underwhelming.\\n\\nHowever, other exhibitions were excellent and detailed. Definitely evident of better research and funding. This is whole day outing with the sheer amount of exhibits available.\\n\\nLockers are available in the museum for easy storage.", "languageCode": "en"}, "rating": 4, "publishTime": "2025-12-28T00:42:17.026835658Z", "originalText": {"text": "eoul’s first permanent Islamic art exhibition features 85 pieces from Qatar’s Museum of Islamic Art, taking visitors through about 1,400 years of Islamic culture, think calligraphy, geometric designs, ceramics, textiles, and architectural details. Honestly, it feels pretty underwhelming.\\n\\nHowever, other exhibitions were excellent and detailed. Definitely evident of better research and funding. This is whole day outing with the sheer amount of exhibits available.\\n\\nLockers are available in the museum for easy storage.", "languageCode": "en"}, "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w4NGFsWnVOelJ0TkU5dVdFaDBXbmxzVFZRM1IzYxAB!2m1!1s0x357ca2ed7e746c37:0x616286c7a66e50e7", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w4NGFsWnVOelJ0TkU5dVdFaDBXbmxzVFZRM1IzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "authorAttribution": {"uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115234753997683339081/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyE7Gwo0az7Js-Te5n_GYHhg-YCxDy6nukqsVkmZqbErma0f05=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4", "displayName": "Yaseera Seedat"}, "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a week ago"}, {"name": "places/ChIJN2x0fu2ifDUR51BupseGYmE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOdGRHRXdabVJJZVc1clUwcHJkV1I2Y2s1RVIzYxAB", "text": {"text": "First time visiting National Museum of Korea.  They had really interesting treasures and art craf