eGCI9Tn=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6", "displayName": "Evelyn C."}, "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 weeks ago"}, {"name": "places/ChIJe4Jbot2ifDUR2zWhruwyaow/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taT1lYSnJkeTEyYkdWS1gyOWpObkJuTkRCbmQxRRAB", "text": {"text": "I super love this spot! 🙌🏼😎 A definite must-visit if you’re in South Korea. The themed cafés, lively vibe, and mix of locals and tourists make it such a memorable experience. You’ll find creative concoctions of drinks, desserts, pastries, and street-food–style snacks alongside main local dishes — definitely not for the sugar or health conscious! 😅. Plus, there are some curated local boutiques and many unpretentious open clothing and accessories stores. Come with an empty stomach and an open mind to enjoy this “village.” I had so much fun exploring and discovering.\\n\\nIt can feel like you are in a small maze — yet you will stumble onto another side street full of unexpected treats or unique little shops. Super fun! Just a tip: when it’s hot, listen to the advice from other visitors’ written comments and prepare 🪭💦🧢. I came when it was around 64°F / 18°C with cloudy skies, and it was perfect. And again, wear comfortable walking shoes 👟! 😉. And have fun! 🤩", "languageCode": "en"}, "rating": 4, "publishTime": "2025-10-12T22:47:16.892309969Z", "originalText": {"text": "I super love this spot! 🙌🏼😎 A definite must-visit if you’re in South Korea. The themed cafés, lively vibe, and mix of locals and tourists make it such a memorable experience. You’ll find creative concoctions of drinks, desserts, pastries, and street-food–style snacks alongside main local dishes — definitely not for the sugar or health conscious! 😅. Plus, there are some curated local boutiques and many unpretentious open clothing and accessories stores. Come with an empty stomach and an open mind to enjoy this “village.” I had so much fun exploring and discovering.\\n\\nIt can feel like you are in a small maze — yet you will stumble onto another side street full of unexpected treats or unique little shops. Super fun! Just a tip: when it’s hot, listen to the advice from other visitors’ written comments and prepare 🪭💦🧢. I came when it was around 64°F / 18°C with cloudy skies, and it was perfect. And again, wear comfortable walking shoes 👟! 😉. And have fun! 🤩", "languageCode": "en"}, "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taT1lYSnJkeTEyYkdWS1gyOWpObkJuTkRCbmQxRRAB!2m1!1s0x357ca2dda25b827b:0x8c6a32ecaea135db", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taT1lYSnJkeTEyYkdWS1gyOWpObkJuTkRCbmQxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "authorAttribution": {"uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101637225463540088196/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocINMI45tn4dsTGrmreXqlc-WHnbNkjL8oUcM_3PMSYhU5W6Uw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5", "displayName": "Monda S."}, "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago"}, {"name": "places/ChIJe4Jbot2ifDUR2zWhruwyaow/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWa1gxQmFWMWQ1WjNSdE9Ha3lWSFpXYVhnNVoxRRAB", "text": {"text": "This is a very nice place to spend a day. It has many traditional and trendy restaurants, and nice cafes, each specializing in a different theme. All the restaurants are nicely decorated and great for taking photos. Korea is a digital payment friendly place, no cash necessary which is great for travellers. We were there on a rainy day and it's still nice.", "languageCode": "en"}, "rating": 5, "publishTime": "2025-10-11T01:47:05.250546404Z", "originalText": {"text": "This is a very nice place to spend a day. It has many traditional and trendy restaurants, and nice cafes, each specializing in a different theme. All the restaurants are nicely decorated and great for taking photos. Korea is a digital payment friendly place, no cash necessary which is great for travellers. We were there on a rainy day and it's still nice.", "languageCode": "en"}